# Calculator Operations

## Add two positive numbers
* Initialize calculator
* Enter number "2"
* Enter number "3"
* Press "add" button
* Result should be "5"

## Subtract numbers
* Initialize calculator
* Enter number "10"
* Enter number "3"
* Press "subtract" button
* Result should be "7"

## Multiply numbers
* Initialize calculator
* Enter number "4"
* Enter number "5"
* Press "multiply" button
* Result should be "20"

## Divide numbers
* Initialize calculator
* Enter number "20"
* Enter number "4"
* Press "divide" button
* Result should be "5"

## Division by zero
* Initialize calculator
* Enter number "10"
* Enter number "0"
* Press "divide" button
* Should see error "cannot divide by zero"

